OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder after
OL,4,Cstabbing mother to death
OL,6,FA man has been convicted of killing
OL,7,Fhis mother after she was found stabbed
OL,8,Fto death in Plymouth last year.
OL,10,FThe body of Debra Cantrell, who was
OL,11,F58, was found at her home on Colwill
OL,12,FRoad, on 31 May 2023.
OL,14,FOfficers were called to the property
OL,15,Ffollowing reports of concern for the
OL,16,Fwelfare of a woman.
