OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder after
OL,4,Cstabbing mother to death
OL,6,FA jury at Plymouth Crown Court heard
OL,7,Fthat Callum Thomas, 33, had been
OL,8,Fviolent towards Debra Cantrell and had
OL,9,Fvoiced threats about killing her "over
OL,10,Fa number of years."
OL,12,FThe court previously heard Thomas
OL,13,Fspent a considerable amount of time
OL,14,Fplaying World War Two games online
OL,15,Fwith a computer gamer in the United
OL,16,FStates.
