OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder after
OL,4,Cstabbing mother to death
OL,6,FThe jury were told that on May 8,
OL,7,Fwhile he was in a hotel in Richmond,
OL,8,FVirginia, the gamer received a message
OL,9,Ffrom Thomas that he had "done
OL,10,Fsomething bad" and he "didn't think he
OL,11,Fwas going to be around for a long
OL,12,Ftime".
OL,14,FThey arranged to meet online later
OL,15,Fthat day and they began online gaming,
OL,16,Fduring which Thomas was "whispering",
OL,17,Fbefore saying he "didn't know" why he
OL,18,Fwas whispering because "the problem
OL,19,Fhad been taken care of" and the
OL,20,F"situation had been dealt with".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
