OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder after
OL,4,Cstabbing mother to death
OL,6,FConcerned, the US gamer rang police in
OL,7,Fthe UK. He told them about Thomas'
OL,8,Fcomments about a problem being "taken
OL,9,Fcare of".
OL,11,FPolice later attended the property and
OL,12,Ffound Ms Cantrell on her bed under a
OL,13,Fduvet, with a fatal knife wound to her
OL,14,Fchest and a pillow over her head.
OL,16,FThomas admitted to the manslaughter of
OL,17,FDebra Cantrell on the basis of
OL,18,Fdiminished responsibility.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
