OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder after
OL,4,Cstabbing mother to death
OL,6,FHowever, prosecutors progressed with
OL,7,Ftheir case, arguing that when he
OL,8,Fkilled his mother he was of sound mind
OL,9,Fand knew what he was doing.
OL,11,FWhile the jury were initially told he
OL,12,Fwas alleged to have fatally stabbed
OL,13,Fher sometime between May 5 and May 31
OL,14,Flast year, evidence suggested that he
OL,15,Fhad more than likely murdered her
OL,16,Fsometime after May 6 or May 7.
OL,18,FAfter finding Thomas guilty of murder,
OL,19,FJudge Peter Johnson thanked the jury
OL,20,Ffor their service.
